    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jean's Beach Restaurant is the best time management game, developed and published by AFEEL.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Recommended for Time Management Game fans.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >★ FEATURES OF THE GAME ★</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Run your own restaurant!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make delicious lobster, salads, drinks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade restaurant and hire employees.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145340/extras/c6efd0b44262359b5da88ac6123f799d.poster.avif?t=1731330732\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145340/extras/c6efd0b44262359b5da88ac6123f799d.webm?t=1731330732\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145340/extras/c6efd0b44262359b5da88ac6123f799d.mp4?t=1731330732\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >★ Story modes ★</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Total 120 levels, 4 unique locations with 30 levels each, 10 unique customer types.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 4 unique locations with 3 types of services.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145340/extras/9403545888a304116a10085715664c66.avif?t=1731330732\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145340/extras_big/9403545888a304116a10085715664c66.avif?t=1731330732 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.